 <title>The Official Unofficial Front End Summit</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/official-unofficial-front-end-summit</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEduIB9MSLz1DNY08/giphy.gif&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Front Enders Unite!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Come join us in the Pauley Atrium for a morning of sharing, discussion and otherwise general Front End Solidarity. All skill levels are welcome!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Note: we&#039;ll hang out for as long as people want to stick around and talk. Definitely at least an hour or more.)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
